               <strong>Note:</strong> HCatStorer does NOT support writing table columns of type smallint or tinyint. 
               To be able to write form Pig using the HCatalog storer, table columns must by of type int or bigint.
               </p>
            </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
            <td>
